Dg">Tam nguyệt hối nhật tống hữu nhân chi An Nam - 三月晦日送友人之安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-B%E1%BB%99t/author-4yoEq5GRUdDDRggLQ7AyqA">Từ Bột</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-d-nlBBRJWy9Xz0rOC3Z-8A">Tây Hồ trúc chi từ kỳ 1 - 西湖竹枝詞其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-Ic-wM4uTt21tJ0mNZjugOA">Thi Nhuận Chương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Vi%C3%AAn-Vi%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc/poem-33CduH4NfT9ibV757snSEw">Viên Viên khúc - 圓圓曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dung/Xu%C3%A2n-du-h%E1%BB%93i-v%C4%83n-thi/poem-YFIj-vYYJTb3lrmUtTaN_g">Xuân du hồi văn thi - 春遊回文詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dung/author-qXPPibIiYGXM8D15wPwoFg">Vương Dung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kwon-Pil/Xu%C3%A2n-giang-t%E1%BB%AB-hi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca/poem-LazQPc3TI7ad2atH4nt5Nw">Xuân giang từ hiệu “Trúc chi ca” - 春江詞效竹枝歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kwon-Pil/author-18yEYxwk0QmM8I02w5pfKQ">Kwon Pil</a>)<br></div>	</div>
